{"tid":190971,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"5種林明禎1次滿足！　一頭「及臀長髮」飄仙味美翻～","createTime":"2017-04-07T13:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-07T16:24:43.000Z","uid":9573,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ef22614be8ef01ca84b43ba2c64d2b9273d37d7a","tid":190971,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:12:05.000Z","msg":"歌手林明禎將在27日發行全新EP《#Me》，新造型7日曝光，她一人分飾五角，以「一人女團」的概念大玩「街頭個性、復古甜美、中性酷率、摩登窈窕、閃亮性感」5大造型，其中一頭及肩波浪長髮、展現摩登窈窕纖腰造型的「金山」，則是小時候奶奶叫她的小名，帶點傳統味的名字，與她現在形象有些反差。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2426/d2426484.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2426%2Fd2426484.jpg&h=26f7fc9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林明禎推出新專輯，自組一人女團。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ze0Q2v.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZe0Q2v.png&h=81463fa2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為了展現多面向的自己，林明禎組成「Me女團」，不管是街頭個性「MinChen」、復古甜美「BB」、摩登窈窕「金山」、閃亮性感「Mickey」、中性酷率「Queen」全由她一人分飾五角演出。其中「BB」，是她每回到香港工作最常被叫的女神代稱，而一頭及肩波浪長髮、展現摩登窈窕纖纖細腰造型的「金山」，則有一個特殊的「兒時回憶」，「金山，是我小時候奶奶叫我的小名，「小時候家人經常叫我金山金山，那時我也是留著一頭快到屁股的長髮！」<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2442/d2442954.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2442%2Fd2442954.jpg&h=00d6dd54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲林明禎新專輯有五種造型。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6vkdnhex\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6vkdnhex&h=858e0d8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n造型中最為狂野奔放，有著一頭爆炸捲長髮的閃亮性感「Mickey」則是求學時代的綽號，「因為我的耳朵大大的，乍看起來很像Mickey Mouse（米老鼠），同學都會開玩笑叫我Mickey。」而女團中最後一個如女王般的造型，是讓林明禎梳起瀏海，展現中性酷率LOOK而取名為「Queen」，則代表她未來想成為如此這般獨當一面的女王。林明禎一次五種造型，也展現不同時期的自己。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2442/d2442955.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2442%2Fd2442955.jpg&h=cc7cddca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼不同造型代表不同時期的林明禎。<br />\n<img src=\"http://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2442/d2442953.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2442%2Fd2442953.jpg&h=0a13d44d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"99bc13833d2fb84ea3257881aaa62ff12e7e5503","tid":190971,"uid":90863,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:13:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"278effbb036a9e65cbf53863907a89c0d1c2be2c","tid":190971,"uid":1249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:15:29.000Z","msg":"Fake ball"},{"pid":"b707f4d20f2a6b0d806e80684a58e24a83983f09","tid":190971,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:38:15.000Z","msg":"假波<br />\n不了。"},{"pid":"26b508cb0c06a4f80dc8e60009e789fc079c7ec3","tid":190971,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:41:54.000Z","msg":"Jed<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13621dc930c495c31ac319c991f76fdc542474fa","tid":190971,"uid":76632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T13:44:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77a2207f204376fe94c96cc844c86f2f6922ba48","tid":190971,"uid":56935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:03:40.000Z","msg":"我份人就好公道既<br />\n法官大人 我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aae248894f6e6f0ceb393da163ec2504d13edd0d","tid":190971,"uid":80792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:35:21.000Z","msg":"西野七瀨正好多"},{"pid":"6c7cc2f420876ccbebe1a5d035d491a7efcec7e6","tid":190971,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"又無校服,又無女僕服,又無OL嬲屌裙<br />\n今次COSPLAY失敗左D"},{"pid":"1a782d4d82a512415fe51c93a11b4957583a502a